CHANGES IN VERSION 1.1.10
-----------------------

UPDATES

    o Support for passing hdf5-backed SummarizedExperiment objects 
      (internal conversion to sparse)
    o Explicitly handle multiple assay() in the summarizedExperiment. Must have
      a named 'counts' assay, or,  just the one unnamed assay.
    

BUG FIXES

    o Subsampling per group should actually be used now.
    

